[A] China: National Health Commission, 83 605 total cases, 4634 deaths
Date: Sun 12 Jul 2020
Source: China National Health Commission [in Chinese, machine trans., abridged, edited]
http://www.nhc.gov.cn/xcs/yqtb/202007/8618a0cea9934f6ab59af2320103a78c.shtml


On 13 Jul 2020 (as of midnight 14 Jul 2020):
- 3 new cases of confirmed infections (all were imported cases into Shanghai municipality), no new cases of suspected infections, and no deaths.
- A total of 1982 imported cases have been reported.
- 83 605 confirmed cases and 4634 deaths; 78 674 recovered and discharged from hospital; 766 903 close contacts with infected patients; and 3267 are under medical observation.
- 5 new asymptomatic cases (all imported); no asymptomatic cases confirmed as symptomatic; 110 asymptomatic cases under medical observation (including 87 imported cases).
- 1469 cases in Hong Kong [an increase of 52 cases since 12 Jul 2020], 46 in Macau.

