[As of 13 Jul 2020, the total number of cases of COVID-19 confirmed in Iran is 259 652, including 13 032 deaths, an increase of 2349 cases and 203 deaths since 12 Jul 2020. From another media report, there are 5 provinces (Lari, Khuzestan, West Azarbaijan, Khorasan Razavi, and Mazandaran) classified as "red zones" and an additional 9 provinces considered in dangerous condition (https://ifpnews.com/irans-covid-19-fatalities-hit-13000-health-ministry).

